{"tid":504593,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【嚴重慎入】【直接出圖】【眼痕捽眼】6 歲 女 雙 眼 又 腫 又 流 血","createTime":"2017-12-20T07:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T02:47:25.000Z","uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"140849bbf749ae5f7a9665c694abf2b9c5e44a60","tid":504593,"uid":24160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:35:49.000Z","msg":"今年11月之前，印度一名6歲女童仲係一個健康活潑嘅小朋友，但上月開始因為眼痕經常「捽眼」，在短短6周內雙眼情況急劇轉壞，雙眼突出紅腫大如網球，且不斷流血，醫生確診她患上癌症，估計只有一成存活機會，連爸爸都不敢正眼望她，體重更由55磅急跌至30磅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/153357_dd280748f50d9abb323728f432fd3d58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F153357_dd280748f50d9abb323728f432fd3d58.jpg&h=86731f25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這名女孩名叫特普拉（Dhanika Tripura），出身於印度東北貧困村落，由上月開始，便因為雙眼痕癢經常擦眼，由於家中貧困，她初時只在村裏看病，只獲止痛藥及抗敏藥治療，但病情急劇惡化，在慈善團體介入下送到新德里醫院治療，確診患上癌症「急性淋巴細胞白血病」（acute lymphocytic leukemia）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/153441_0be4d2fd1dd7ced148dd9519b2652cda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F153441_0be4d2fd1dd7ced148dd9519b2652cda.jpg&h=fbb200c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醫生估計，她的情況有生命危險，特普拉的生存機會僅得一成，院方目前已開始為她進行化療，但可能還需要標靶藥及類固醇治療。爸爸希望外界可以伸出援手，他說：「我沒有讀過書，我太窮了，連送子女上學的能力也沒有&hellip;&hellip;我們現在真的很擔心她的生命。」特普拉的父親只是一名普通工人，月薪僅1000盧比（105港元），媽媽是家庭主婦，全家都只靠父親微薄的收入為生，根本無力支付高昂的醫療費用。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/153526_445ff46dcd3405f28de63bc8ac31cc22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F153526_445ff46dcd3405f28de63bc8ac31cc22.jpg&h=351beaec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n捐款網址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://milaap.org/fundrais......oard&amp;mlp_referrer_id=519199\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmilaap.org%2Ffundrais......oard%26mlp_referrer_id%3D519199&d=Xg0MilhLFswsUtwzR4mAVGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=f953a0df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://milaap.org/fundrais......oard&amp;mlp_referrer_id=519199</a><br />\n<br />\n資料來源: 英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%9C%BC%E7%97%95%E6%8D%BD%E7%9C%BC-6%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E9%9B%99%E7%9C%BC%E5%8F%88%E8%85%AB%E5%8F%88%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%80-033109738.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%259C%25BC%25E7%2597%2595%25E6%258D%25BD%25E7%259C%25BC-6%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E9%259B%2599%25E7%259C%25BC%25E5%258F%2588%25E8%2585%25AB%25E5%258F%2588%25E6%25B5%2581%25E8%25A1%2580-033109738.html&d=Xg0MilhLFswsUtwzR4mAVGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=61556297\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%9C%BC%E7%97%95%E6%8D%BD%E7%9C%BC-6%E6%AD%B2%E5%A5%B3%E9%9B%99%E7%9C%BC%E5%8F%88%E8%85%AB%E5%8F%88%E6%B5%81%E8%A1%80-033109738.html</a>"},{"pid":"33fc60dbc723fe3bd6416432292af470dc3a4eee","tid":504593,"uid":40867,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:48:25.000Z","msg":"由佢啦<br />\n係呢d地方生存就唔好繁殖啦"},{"pid":"8b262d2418bde5a0cadee3dd4512b7271f319b5e","tid":504593,"uid":29080,"like":50,"dislike":3,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:51:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/155041_f334f980ef467d4525375f2cb0e690f8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F155041_f334f980ef467d4525375f2cb0e690f8.jpeg&h=74abb7d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd772e74721b9300c6d6c32934e2b8b0240a8525","tid":504593,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:51:04.000Z","msg":"細路女好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceac411df421a7d73b91a6060c6ad75b1746d9e5","tid":504593,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T07:54:09.000Z","msg":"唔小心笑左, 捽眼捽到咁真係世界級 <img 