":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/155041_f334f980ef467d4525375f2cb0e690f8.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F155041_f334f980ef467d4525375f2cb0e690f8.jpeg&h=74abb7d1&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪咁賤啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我都笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唉， 應該係細菌感染，印度農村好多菌"}]}